                  </hi>. I am the witness's wife. I remember the prisoner coming to our lodging, in king-street, one sunday—I saw him again on the Tuesday, between eight and nine o'clock at night—he took away books in a bag.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. ADOLPHUS</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> You never saw him before that Sunday? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No; nor after that Tuesday—I saw him on the Monday in Princes-street—the books had been in my lodgings a week, I suppose, be<lb></lb>fore he came on the Sunday.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18351214-name-607" type="witnessName">
