                  </hi>. I am a bookseller, and live at No.158, High Hol<lb></lb>born. I was in treaty with the prisoner for some books—I received a letter from him—this is it—I agreed to purchase that lot for 31<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.—Canning's speeches in quires, and Erskine's in quires and boarded, and other books—I sold them for 36<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. about two days after.</p>
